quran[8{c,v,t}:
17,59,aur hum ko nishanain bhejnay se nahi roka magar is baat ne ke inn se pehlay ke log unn ko jhutla chuke hain ( chunancha dekh lau ) smod ko hum ne alania oontni laa kar di aur onhon ne is par zulm kya hum nishanain isi liye to bhaijtay hain ke log inhen dekh kar dareen
17,60,"yaad karo ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne tum se keh diya tha ke tairay rab ne inn logon ko ghair rakha hai aur yeh jo kuch abhi hum ne tumhe dekhaya hai, iss ko aur uss darakht ko jis par quran mein laanat ki gayi hai, hum ne inn logon ke liye bas aik fitnah bana kar rakh diya hum aِnhin tanbeeh par tanbeeh kiye ja rahay hain, magar har tanbeeh inn ki sir kashi hi mein izafah kiye jati hai"
17,61,"aur yaad karo jabkay hum ne mulaika se kaha ke aadam ko sajda karo, to sab ne sajda kya, magar iblees ne nah kya a seen ne kaha"" kya mein uss ko sajda karoon jisay to ne matti se banaya hai? """
17,62,"phir woh bola"" dekh to sahi, kya yeh is qabil tha ke to ne isay mujh par fazeelat di? agar to mujhe qayamat ke din taq mohlat day to mein is ki poori nasal ki beekh kinny kar daloon, bas thoray hi log mujh se bach saken ge """
17,63,"Allah taala ne farmaya"" acha to ja, un mein se jo bhi teri pairwi karen, tujh sameit unn sab ke liye jahannum hi bharpoor jaza hai"
17,64,"to jis jis ko apni dawat se phsla sakta hai phsla le, un par apne sawaar aur payaday charha laa, maal aur aulaad mein un ke sath sajha laga, aur un ko wadon ke jaal mein phaans aur shetan ke waday aik dhokay ke siwa aur kuch bhi nahi"
17,65,"yaqeenan mere bundon par tujhe koi Iqtidaar haasil nah hoga, aur tawakkal ke liye tera rab kaafi hai """
17,66,tumhara ( haqeeqi ) rab to woh hai jo samandar mein tumhari kashti chalata hai taakay tum is ka fazl tala sh karo haqeeqat yeh hai ke woh tumahray haal par nihayat meharban hai
